data.description: Perfect location next to MTSU, this end-unit townhome as seen a recent facelift with fresh paint, brand new carpet upstairs, and also includes a like-new LG washer/dryer set that will convey with the property. The vinyl hardwood downstairs combined with the open floorplan give the home an extra nice feel that is not common with other townhome units of this caliber in Murfreesboro. As well, both bedrooms upstairs have their own walk-in closet with en-suite bathroom. DON'T MISS THIS ONE!
